Somehow,
the
oneness
of
this
shared
experience,
the
coalescing
of
millions
of
minds,
had
affected
the
randomizing
function
of
these
machines,
organizing
their
outputs
and
bringing
order
from
chaos.
The
shocking
discovery,
it
seemed,
paralleled
the
ancient
spiritual
belief
in
a
"cosmic
consciousness"
a
vast
coalescing
of
human
intention
that
was
actually
capable
