Lynne
McTaggart
described
it,
was
a
substance
outside
the
confines
of
the
body
a
highly
ordered
energy
capable
of
changing
the
physical
world.
Katherine
had
been
fascinated
by
McTaggart'
s
book
The
Intention
Experiment,
and
her
global,
Web-based
study
theintentionexperiment.com
aimed
at
discovering
how
human
intention
could
affect
the
world.
A
